plot: Calling all patriots! Let's show Homelander we've got his back and we're not going to let Starlight and her House of Horrors get away with trafficking children and drinking their adrenaline! It's time for real Americans to fight back! Join the Hometeamers and Stormchasers tomorrow at Vought Square! Stand back and stand by!

Butcher takes Soldier Boy to Vought Tower so that the latter can fulfill his promise and help take down Homelander. But Soldier Boy has learned about his past and the part Homelander plays in it., and has second thoughts. Meanwhile, Annie and Maeve join up with the reunited Boys to take down Soldier Boy no matter what Butcher's deal is.—Gislef
